    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/extras/ebc005cf83d67427f03e43b8a3e64009.avif?t=1730140030\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>The Ministry's vaults store digital copies of every person. To investigate a simple murder, it would be enough to just talk to the victim's copy. However, for a case of national importance, you'll have to use the most recent and most terrifying technological advancements.<br><br>Plug someone's brain scan into one device and have a peaceful chat with them on neutral ground.<br><br>Plug them into something a little more unorthodox and see how they behave under pressure.<br><br>I could say that the choice is yours, but that would be a lie—you will have to get your hands dirty one way or another.<br><br>A short (1-2 hour) linear narrative puzzle based on dialogues, plugging wires into devices, and messing with switches. If you always thought that the ending of 1984 could use a little more wiring puzzles, then this is the game for you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/extras/d94373ce804771dda5e17d2dc4eb7567.poster.avif?t=1730140030\" width=608 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/extras/d94373ce804771dda5e17d2dc4eb7567.webm?t=1730140030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/extras/d94373ce804771dda5e17d2dc4eb7567.mp4?t=1730140030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/extras/6b6e38b66fe6dc7074e8de7edb1888e2.poster.avif?t=1730140030\" width=608 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.ak